erv\" title=\"Nerv\">Nerv</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Pilot(s)\n</th>\n<td>\n</td></tr>\n\n<tr>\n<th>Unique Properties\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/S%C2%B2_Engine\" title=\"S² Engine\">S² Engine</a> Testbed\n</td></tr>\n\n\n<tr>\n<th>Debut\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/ANIMA\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"ANIMA\">Backstory of Anima Vol.1</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Status\n</th>\n<td>Destroyed\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><br />\nLike <a href=\"/Evangelion_Unit-03\" title=\"Evangelion Unit-03\">its TV counterpart</a>, Unit-03 was destroyed during its activation test. A notable difference in design is that unlike either of its counterparts, the S² Engine is an attachment to the back that is visible from the outside.\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260416191620\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.011 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.014 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 61/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1688/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 234/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 4/100\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    6.934      1 -total\n 39.07%    2.709      1 Template:Expand\n 37.16%    2.577      1 Template:Stub\n 22.28%    1.545      1 Template:Evangelion_Rebuild_Infobox\n 16.79%    1.164      2 Template:Br\n 16.25%    1.127      2 Template:-\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key mediawikidb-ew_:pcache:idhash:55649-0!canonical and timestamp 20260416191620 and revision id 114348. Rendering was triggered because: page-view\n -->\n</div>", "summary": "NGE NTE Anima Other  Figures", "sections": [], "categories": [], "infobox": {"name": "Evangelion Unit-04", "image": "[[Image:Anima 04.png|center|225px]]", "japanese": "エヴァンゲリオン４号機", "model": "Production Model", "nation": "US", "organization": "[[Nerv]]", "unique": "[[S² Engine]] Testbed